<p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">当迷彩与青春碰撞，当镜头与公益相拥，经济管理学院于11月6日晚举办“新颜映迷彩，光影述青春”公益摄影大赛颁奖仪式。138幅优秀作品脱颖而出，用光影定格热血瞬间、传递公益温度。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011487646.png" alt="1763011487646.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011487646.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">经济管理学院学工办主任郭伟首先对摄影大赛的圆满落幕表示祝贺。他提到，每一幅作品都以独特视角诠释了青春的多元模样，以镜头传递了公益的温暖力量。希望同学们能永葆对生活的热爱与感知，让光影成为记录成长、传递正能量的载体。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011611649.png" alt="1763011611649.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011611649.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011635870.png" alt="1763011635870.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011635870.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011658771.png" alt="1763011658771.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011658771.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011679970.png" alt="1763011679970.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011679970.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011695737.png" alt="1763011695737.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011695737.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011751811.png" alt="1763011751811.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011751811.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011785006.png" alt="1763011785006.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011785006.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">获奖代表上台分享创作心路，他谈到，在拍摄过程中不仅用镜头捕捉到了迷彩服下的青春活力，更在记录中读懂了公益的深层意义。这份荣誉既是鼓励也是动力，未来将继续用镜头发现美好、传递温暖，让更多人感受青春与公益的碰撞之美。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011816666.png" alt="1763011816666.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011816666.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">此次颁奖仪式不仅是对优秀摄影作品的表彰，更是对青年学子创意与担当的致敬。经济管理学院将以此次活动为契机，持续搭建文化育人、实践育人的优质平台，深耕青春正能量传播，助力学子在多元实践中绽放光彩。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011851410.png" alt="1763011851410.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763011851410.png" style="width: 50%;"></p>